A vast, dimly lit server room rendered in cyberpunk style, with towering racks of glowing databases stretching into the distance. In the foreground, a lone hooded figure stands before a massive holographic display showing intricate geometric patterns representing database architecture. Streams of neon-blue data particles are violently fragmenting and dissolving into digital dust, swirling away like ash in wind. The scene has a dramatic, ominous atmosphere with deep purple shadows, electric cyan highlights, and streaks of warning-red light cutting through the haze. Cables hang like vines from the ceiling, some sparking. The holographic interface shows complex nested structures being systematically erased, leaving empty wireframe shells behind. The mood is both destructive and cleansing, capturing the dangerous power of wiping a system clean.
